It's a night-version of the best Counter-Strike:Source "fy_" Map ever.
I changed the skybox into a beatyful nightskybox, 
changed the light of the map and fixed some bugs.


Changes:
- add beatyful skybox
- add moonligt
- add spawnpoints (now 40)
- remove some prob_physic's
- optimize some brushwork

I hope you like it^^
